function adminClearNotifications(){ modalShow({title:'Konfirmasi', body:'Hapus semua notifikasi inbox admin?', actions:[{label:'Batal',kind:'secondary'},{label:'Hapus Semua',kind:'danger',onClick: async ()=>{ toast('Menghapus notifikasi...'); try{ await apiCall('adminClearNotifications',{}); toast('Inbox admin berhasil dibersihkan'); adminRefreshNotifications(); adminRefreshNotificationsQuick(); }catch(err){ modalShow({title:'Gagal', body:escapeHtml(err?.message||err)}); } }}]}); }
async function adminLoadUsers(){ const status=document.getElementById('adminStatus'); if(status) status.textContent='Memuat daftar pengguna...'; try{ const res=await apiCall('adminListUsers',{}); const rows=res?.list||[]; if(status) status.textContent=`Total user: ${rows.length}`; renderAdminUsers(rows); }catch(err){ if(status) status.textContent='Error: ' + (err?.message||err); }}
function renderAdminUsers(list){ const box=document.getElementById('adminUsersTable'); if(!box) return; if(!list?.length){ box.innerHTML='<div class="hint">Belum ada data pengguna.</div>'; return; } let html='<table><tr><th>Username</th><th>NIP</th><th>Nama</th><th>Email</th><th>Role Saat Ini</th><th>Ubah Role</th><th>Aksi</th></tr>'; (list||[]).forEach(u=>{ const rawUsername=String(u.username||''), safeUsername=rawUsername.replace(/'/g,"\\'"), safeNip=String(u.nip||'').replace(/'/g,"\\'"), currentRole=String(u.role||'user').toLowerCase(), roleSelId='roleSel_'+rawUsername.replace(/[^a-zA-Z0-9_]/g,'_'); html += `<tr><td>${escapeHtml(rawUsername)}</td><td>${escapeHtml(u.nip||'')}</td><td>${escapeHtml(u.nama||'')}</td><td>${escapeHtml(u.email||'')}</td><td>${escapeHtml(currentRole)}</td><td><div style="display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; align-items:center;"><select id="${roleSelId}" style="min-width:140px;"><option value="user" ${currentRole==='user'?'selected':''}>user</option><option value="sekretaris" ${currentRole==='sekretaris'?'selected':''}>sekretaris</option><option value="admin" ${currentRole==='admin'?'selected':''}>admin</option></select><button type="button" class="secondary" style="margin-top:0; padding:6px 10px;" onclick="adminChangeRoleFromList('${safeUsername}')">Simpan Role</button></div></td><td><button type="button" class="secondary" style="margin-top:0; padding:6px 10px;" onclick="adminResetPassFromList('${safeUsername}')">Reset</button><button type="button" class="danger" style="margin-top:0; padding:6px 10px;" onclick="adminDeleteUserFromList('${safeNip}')">Hapus</button></td></tr>`; }); html+='</table>'; box.innerHTML=html; }
window.adminChangeRoleFromList = async function(username){ const elId='roleSel_'+String(username||'').replace(/[^a-zA-Z0-9_]/g,'_'); const role=document.getElementById(elId)?.value||'user'; toast('Menyimpan role...'); try{ await apiCall('adminUpdateUserRole',{username,role}); toast('Role berhasil diperbarui'); adminLoadUsers(); }catch(err){ modalShow({title:'Gagal ubah role', body:escapeHtml(err?.message||err)}); }};
async function adminCreateUser(){ const nama=(document.getElementById('newUserNama')?.value||'').trim(), username=(document.getElementById('newUserUsername')?.value||'').trim(), nip=(document.getElementById('newUserNip')?.value||'').trim(), email=(document.getElementById('newUserEmail')?.value||'').trim(), pass=document.getElementById('newUserPass')?.value||'', role=document.getElementById('newUserRole')?.value||'user'; toast('Membuat user...'); try{ await apiCall('adminCreateUser',{nama,username,nip,email,password:pass,role}); toast('User berhasil dibuat'); ['newUserNama','newUserUsername','newUserNip','newUserEmail','newUserPass'].forEach(id=>document.getElementById(id).value=''); adminLoadUsers(); }catch(err){ modalShow({title:'Error', body:escapeHtml(err?.message||err)}); }}
window.adminResetPassFromList = function(username){ modalShow({title:'Reset Password', body:`<div class="hint">Reset password untuk username: <b>${escapeHtml(username)}</b></div><label for="rpNewPass">Password Baru</label><input id="rpNewPass" type="password" placeholder="Masukkan password baru">`, actions:[{label:'Batal',kind:'secondary'},{label:'Reset', onClick: async ()=>{ const pass=document.getElementById('rpNewPass')?.value||''; toast('Mereset password...'); try{ await apiCall('adminResetPassword',{username,newPassword:pass}); toast('Password berhasil direset'); adminLoadUsers(); }catch(err){ modalShow({title:'Error', body:escapeHtml(err?.message||err)}); } }}]}); };
window.adminDeleteUserFromList = function(nipOrUsername){ modalShow({title:'Konfirmasi', body:`Hapus user <b>${escapeHtml(nipOrUsername)}</b>?`, actions:[{label:'Batal',kind:'secondary'},{label:'Hapus',kind:'danger',onClick: async ()=>{ toast('Menghapus user...'); try{ await apiCall('adminDeleteUser',{nip:nipOrUsername}); toast('User berhasil dihapus'); adminLoadUsers(); }catch(err){ modalShow({title:'Error', body:escapeHtml(err?.message||err)}); } }}]}); };
async function adminRefreshUploadRoot(){ const hint=document.getElementById('uploadRootHint'); if(hint) hint.textContent='Memuat root folder...'; try{ const res=await apiCall('adminGetUploadRoot',{}); document.getElementById('uploadRootId').value=res?.folderId||''; if(hint) hint.innerHTML=res?.url ? `Root aktif: <a href="${res.url}" target="_blank">${res.url}</a>` : ''; }catch(err){ if(hint) hint.textContent='Error: ' + (err?.message||err); }}
